  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick and play any level! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful soundtrack! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >16 types of subgames! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make gameplay easier with the Hint funtion! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trivia about the USA!</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>Collector's Edition</h1><p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >39 extra levels </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music Player </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wallpapers</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the wisdom of the founding fathers through intriguing puzzles featuring quotes from the visionaries who shaped a nation. Test your knowledge of famous Americans as you unravel clues and unlock fascinating anecdotes about iconic figures who left an indelible mark on history. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/203aa3f2a510020d5f81c26bc317e35f.poster.avif?t=1729572852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/203aa3f2a510020d5f81c26bc317e35f.webm?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/203aa3f2a510020d5f81c26bc317e35f.mp4?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the beauty of America's landscapes through mesmerizing jigsaw puzzles featuring breathtaking locations from sea to shining sea. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/8f83c9b8bdf52216dbc75a39a3177710.poster.avif?t=1729572852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/8f83c9b8bdf52216dbc75a39a3177710.webm?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/8f83c9b8bdf52216dbc75a39a3177710.mp4?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every challenge, Stars, Stripes, and Subgames ensures a patriotic celebration of American heritage, culture, and ingenuity.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the wisdom of the founding fathers through intriguing puzzles featuring quotes from the visionaries who shaped a nation. Test your knowledge of famous Americans as you unravel clues and unlock fascinating anecdotes about iconic figures who left an indelible mark on history. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/203aa3f2a510020d5f81c26bc317e35f.poster.avif?t=1729572852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/203aa3f2a510020d5f81c26bc317e35f.webm?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/203aa3f2a510020d5f81c26bc317e35f.mp4?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the beauty of America's landscapes through mesmerizing jigsaw puzzles featuring breathtaking locations from sea to shining sea. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/8f83c9b8bdf52216dbc75a39a3177710.poster.avif?t=1729572852\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/8f83c9b8bdf52216dbc75a39a3177710.webm?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428470/extras/8f83c9b8bdf52216dbc75a39a3177710.mp4?t=1729572852\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every challenge, Stars, Stripes, and Subgames ensures a patriotic celebration of American heritage, culture, and ingenuity.</p>",
